THE GAME
--------

  'SunMaze' is a Workbench game where you must place mirrors to
reflect the sun's ray, so it gets to an arrival position, located
somewhere in the labyrinth. To complicate matters a little, only
a small portion (a 5 by 5 space area) of the labyrinth is shown...

  To move, click on the arrow tiles located at the edge of the
game board or by using the cursor keys.

  Have fun!

FEATURES
--------

-Simple installation: just run the game and play!

-A game you can play while waiting for other tasks to complete...
 or just for fun!

-Small package, the Lha archive is smaller than 50 kilobytes, so
 it doesn't take ages to download ...although, you can play
 another of my Workbench games while downloading this game ;)

-The game plays on the Workbench screen and its window is
 resizeable.

